DESCRIPTIONS.description: Kenneth is your typical nerdy human male, recently graduated from high school and ready to move on to college to prepare for the rest of his life. But, due to an unfortunate mix-up, he finds himself enrolled in a college for furs! No problem, right? A college is a college. But when an upperclassmen bully sets her sights on him as her next target for torment, he may find that his unconventional college won't do as well as he thought.
